oms. Each room includes daily housekeeping, a DVD player, a microwave, a mini-fridge and plush robes. The studios have kitchenettes and sleeper sofas, while suites feature spacious lounge areas with sofa sleepers. Other services include free DVD rentals, a 24-hour front desk, meeting and banquet space. McKenney\'s at The Inn serves casual fare on-site. Unwind in the outdoor hot tub and heated pool, or work out in the fitness center. The hotel is two miles from downtown Aspen, tucked into the base of Buttermilk Ski Resort. Snap into your skis in winter or hit the hiking trails in summer at Snowmass Village, about 15 minutes away by car. Other activities in winter include dog sledding, snowmobiling and sleigh rides. Come summertime, the Aspen Golf Club, directly across from the hotel, and the biking trails around Buttermilk Mountain are perfect for family outings. The hotel is one-and-a-half miles from Aspen/Pitkin County Airport, 125 miles from Grand Junction Regional Airport and 181 miles from Denver International Airport. Priceline guests appreciate The Inn at Aspen by Wyndham Vacation Rentals for its &quot;great&quot; location, &quot;large&quot; rooms and &quot;friendly and helpful&quot; staff. ','[\"Air conditioning\",\"Alarm clock\",\"Banquet facilities\",\"Cable television\",\"Car rental desk\",\"Cocktail lounge\",\"Coin operated laundry\"]','[\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/402/40279247.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/402/40279244.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/402/40279249.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/402/40279250.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/402/40279256.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/402/40279260.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/402/40279264.jpg\"]'),(4,'Bed & Breakfast On Broadway',NULL,'BUSINESS_LIKE',218.99,182.99,4,'722 Broadway Avenue East','Seattle','WA','98102','+1206-329-8933','US','This inn is located 2 miles from downtown Seattle and the Seattle Art Museum. Bed and Breakfast on Broadway serves a light continental breakfast consisting of baked goods, assorted juice, and hot beverages. Rooms are equipped with free Wi-Fi.Each uniquely designed room features bright colors, various art works and a seating area. All rooms have a clock radio and a private bathroom. For added convenience a TV, hairdryer and ironing facilities are provided.The Broadway Bed and Breakfast offers a comfortable dining room and common area that includes a grand piano for guests to play. Outside, the property boasts a beautiful garden and patio seating. The 100% smoke-free inn provides free parking.Pike Place Market, hosting an extensive variety of local vendors, is a 9-minute drive from Bed and Breakfast on Broadway. The inn is 1.4 miles from Seattle University. ','[\"Air conditioning\",\"Alarm clock\",\"Banquet facilities\",\"Cable television\",\"Car rental desk\",\"Cocktail lounge\",\"Coin operated laundry\"]','[\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/350/3509377.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/291/29179211.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/291/29179212.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/291/29179213.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/291/29179215.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/291/29179218.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/350/3509361.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/350/3509362.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/350/3509363.jpg\"]'),(5,'Doubletree By Hilton Williamsburg',NULL,'FAMILY_LIKE',118.99,91.99,4,'50 Kingsmill Road','Williamsburg','VA','23185','757-220-2500','US','On-site dining, an indoor/outdoor swimming pool, 24-hour fitness and business centers, plus spacious, comfy accommodations, await Priceline guests at the non-smoking DoubleTree by Hilton Williamsburg. The six-story property has 295 spacious rooms that feature stylish decor and modern amenities, including 37-inch HDTVs, available high-speed internet access, in-room coffeemakers and generous work spaces with plush club chairs. Some suites also include separate living and sleeping areas. Guests enjoy homelike comforts and Southern hospitality at the Doubletree By Hilton with warm chocolate chip cookies available upon arrival. The hotel has over 48,000-square-feet of meeting and event space, a 24-hour business center and on-site audiovisual support. There is an auditorium, amphitheater and 30 additional meeting rooms for a high-tech conference or board meeting, while the ballroom also provides an ideal setting for weddings or receptions. In the morning, guests can enjoy a breakfast buffet in the Harvest Grille Dining Room, or order snacks and beverages while surfing the web in the internet cafe. Later on in the day, Pitcher\'s offers pub fare and hand-crafted cocktails, as well as the perfect spot to watch your favorite sports team on the large LED flat-panel TVs. There is also a 24-hour fitness center, an indoor/outdoor swimming pool and a beautifully landscaped poolside courtyard. The hotel is adjacent to I-64 and I-199. It\'s two miles from Busch Gardens and 10 minutes by car to Colonial Williamsburg. World-famous golfing, dining and shops (including Prime Outlets shopping mall), as well as William and Mary College, are all located nearby. It\'s 15 minutes to Yorktown Victory Center and Jamestown Settlement. Norfolk International Airport is 40 miles away; Newport News/Williamsburg International Airport is 15 miles from the hotel. Plenty of on-site amenities and a stellar location for visiting Colonial Williamsburg are among the perks Priceline guests enjoy at DoubleTtree by Hilton Williamsburg. ','[\"Air conditioning\",\"Alarm clock\",\"Banquet facilities\",\"Cable television\",\"Car rental desk\",\"Cocktail lounge\",\"Coin operated laundry\"]','[\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/214/21471169.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/183/18343225.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/183/18343226.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/183/18343228.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/203/20344785.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/203/20344801.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/203/20344834.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/214/21471162.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/214/21471163.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/214/21471164.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/214/21471165.jpg\"]'),(6,'Hotel Metropolis',NULL,'TRENDY',118.99,91.99,4,'25 Mason Street','San Francisco','CA','94102','415-775-4600','US','Located in a lively, central downtown locale, with free Wi-Fi, flat-panel TVs, a library, and fitness and business centers, the Hotel Metropolis is a Golden Gate winner with our guests. This 1930s 10-story hotel features 105 cozy rooms with themes of earth, wind, fire, or water. Each offers a flat-panel TV with Nintendo and pay movies, free Wi-Fi, a desk, and a mini-fridge. The onsite gym and business centers are both open 24/7. If you need some downtime, grab a book in the library or a breather in the meditation room. A concierge is on staff, and on-site laundry and dry cleaning facilities are also available. Leave the car with the valet (for a fee). One block from Market Street, the hotel is located in the heart of downtown\'s Theatre District and Union Square, and within a walking distance to myriad dining options and shops including the Westfield San Francisco Centre. The Powell Street Cable Car line is only one block away, and a 30-minute ride will lead you to the airport via the Powell Street BART (Bay Area Rapid Transit) rail system, a short five-minute walk east. If you\'re in town for business, grab a cab to the Moscone Convention Center, less than 10 minutes east. Or for a wild night on the town, check out nearby clubs within a 10-minute walk. The Hotel Metropolis offers our guests a convenient downtown location that\'s easy on the wallet and solid on the amenities. Now that\'s a negotiation. ','[\"Air conditioning\",\"Alarm clock\",\"Banquet facilities\",\"Cable television\",\"Car rental desk\",\"Cocktail lounge\",\"Coin operated laundry\"]','[\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091986.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091937.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091939.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091947.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091949.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091976.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091988.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091994.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46091998.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46092003.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46092004.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46092013.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46092442.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46093041.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46098432.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46098444.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/460/46098446.jpg\"]'),(7,'Andaz Napa - A Concept By Hyatt',NULL,'LUXURIOUS',218.99,191.99,4,'1450 First Street','Napa','CA','94559','707-224-3900','US','Boutique rooms with plush beds, 42-inch LCD TVs and a downtown Napa location make the non-smoking Andaz Napa - a concept by Hyatt a fantastic choice for Priceline guests. The sleek, contemporary hotel is a five-floor building that\'s home to 141 spacious rooms adorned with hickory hardwood floors, chocolate leather headboards, plush rugs and rich colors. Accommodations boast marble bathrooms, waterfall showers, 42-inch, flat-panel LCD TVs with premium cable, iPod docking stations, Wi-Fi (for a fee), and plush beds with pillowtop mattresses, Italian-cotton matelasse coverlets and crisp, cotton-rich sheets. Some rooms have balconies with views of downtown and the river, and some have jetted tubs and/or sofa beds. The hotel also has a wine bar, a restaurant featuring local ingredients and an outdoor terrace with a hardwood deck, a fire pit, porch swings, lounge chairs and vine-draped niches. Parking is available for an additional fee. The hotel is on First Street in the West End of downtown, about a half-mile southwest of Oxbow Public Market. If you\'re driving up from the Bay Area, the hotel is 51 miles north of Oakland International Airport and 59 miles north of San Francisco International Airport. The &quot;very nice boutique&quot; Andaz Napa - a concept by Hyatt strikes Priceline guests as &quot;visually attractive,&quot; with a &quot;fabulous outdoor deck&quot; and a &quot;good location.&quot; ','[\"Air conditioning\",\"Alarm clock\",\"Banquet facilities\",\"Cable television\",\"Car rental desk\",\"Cocktail lounge\",\"Coin operated laundry\"]','[\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/448/44881342.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/448/44881344.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/448/44881345.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/448/44881346.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/448/44881347.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/448/44881348.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/448/44881349.jpg\"]'),(8,'Crosby Street Hotel',NULL,'BOUTIQUEY',218.99,191.99,4,'79 Crosby Street','New York','NY','10012','+1212-226-6400','US','Located on a cobbled street in the SoHo neighborhood, this contemporary design hotel features a beautiful inner courtyard and an on-site terrace restaurant. Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the hotel.The Crosby Street Hotel offers bright, modern rooms with high ceilings and full-length windows. Each is equipped with flat-screen cable TV, DVD player and iPod docking station.Guests of Crosby Street are welcome to work out in the 24-hour gym or relax in front of the fireplace in the plush drawing room. Films are shown in the hotel\'s private theater each Sunday.The Crosby Bar and Terrace serves gourmet items including breakfast and brunch. An afternoon tea with pastries and sandwiches is offered daily.The Crosby Street Hotel is adjacent to the Museum of Modern Art Design and 1 block from the Spring Street subway station. ','[\"Air conditioning\",\"Alarm clock\",\"Banquet facilities\",\"Cable television\",\"Car rental desk\",\"Cocktail lounge\",\"Coin operated laundry\"]','[\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350336.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350339.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350342.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350350.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350352.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350353.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350356.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350363.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/333/33350419.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/483/48351636.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/483/48351639.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/483/48351669.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/483/48351671.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/483/48351681.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/483/48351682.jpg\"]'),(9,'Sheraton Kona Resort And Spa At Keauhou Bay',NULL,'BEACHY',118.99,101.99,4,'78-128 Ehukai Street','Kailua Kona','HI','96740','808-930-4900','US','Offering oceanfront views, a landscaped outdoor pool area, on-site dining, gifts shops and a day spa, the Sheraton Kona Resort And Spa At Keauhou Bay is a family-friendly retreat close to snorkeling and golfing. Set on a dramatic outcropping of volcanic rock overlooking the Pacific, the three-floor Sheraton boasts 519 rooms with private balconies, cable TVs, mini-fridges and Wi-Fi (included in the resort fee). On-site dining options include a seafood restaurant, a casual cafe, a poolside grill and a cocktail lounge with ocean views and live entertainment. The centerpiece of the lush grounds is a giant freeform pool with slides, fountains and two hot tubs set among rocks and plantings. Other activities include volleyball, tennis, basketball, a fitness center and a weekly luau. Guests also enjoy spa services and on-site gift shops. Parking is available for a fee. Central Kailua Kona is seven miles from the Sheraton. Kahalu\'u Beach Park is five minutes away, and golf at Kona Country Club is three minutes away. Kona International Airport is 15 miles from the hotel, and Hawaii Volcanoes National Park is about 45 miles away. Priceline guests say they &quot;love&quot; the dramatic location of the &quot;great-for-families&quot; Sheraton Kona Resort And Spa At Keauhou Bay, which impresses with its &quot;enthusiastic staff,&quot; &quot;fun activities (like hula classes)&quot; and blockbuster outdoor pool with &quot;cool&quot; water slides and hot tubs.  ','[\"Air conditioning\",\"Alarm clock\",\"Banquet facilities\",\"Cable television\",\"Car rental desk\",\"Cocktail lounge\",\"Coin operated laundry\"]','[\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/115/11574522.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/108/1081865.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/108/1081868.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/108/1081869.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/108/1081873.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/108/1081874.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/775/7756394.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/115/11552642.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/max500/115/11552643.jpg\",\"http://aff.bstatic.com/images/hotel/m